WEBVTT

01:34.400 --> 01:36.920
MAIN TITLE

03:02.040 --> 03:04.120
Don't blame me.
Don't blame me. Don't blame me.

03:48.200 --> 03:51.320
EPISODE TITLE

03:51.400 --> 03:57.400
XINYA FASHION, CASUAL WEAR

04:07.280 --> 04:10.480
YONG'S FASHION

04:20.240 --> 04:22.280
PERSON IN CHARGE: SUN ZHENGYONG

04:25.600 --> 04:27.240
Young man, is Mr. Sun around?

04:27.320 --> 04:28.360
I want to pick up some stock.

04:28.440 --> 04:29.360
He's gone out to restock.

04:29.960 --> 04:32.240
-When did he leave?
-No idea.

04:32.320 --> 04:34.440
If you're picking up goods,
leave your pager number.

04:48.040 --> 04:50.000
CLOSED TODAY, JUNE 30TH

04:50.080 --> 04:50.920
Young man,

04:51.640 --> 04:54.400
why is the shop closed on June 30th?

04:54.480 --> 04:55.840
No idea.

04:57.120 --> 04:58.760
Whatever I ask, you don't know.

04:58.840 --> 05:00.000
Do you work here?

05:00.080 --> 05:02.760
Mister, I only started two days ago.

05:02.840 --> 05:04.200
I haven't even seen the boss.

05:04.280 --> 05:06.160
-You've never seen him?
-No.

05:06.240 --> 05:08.320
-Where did he go?
-No idea.

05:09.640 --> 05:11.040
His wife told me

05:11.120 --> 05:12.560
to tell anyone who asks where he is
that he's out restocking.

05:12.640 --> 05:15.400
If they ask when he'll be back,
just say I don't know.

05:15.480 --> 05:17.080
So I really don't know.

05:30.800 --> 05:33.200
I'm from the Nanshan Branch.
I'm here to ask a few questions.

05:33.840 --> 05:35.960
Hello, Officer. I'm Jessica.
How can I help?

05:36.040 --> 05:37.040
JESSICA

05:37.120 --> 05:39.720
I'd like to check
the sales record for this dress.

05:40.480 --> 05:42.480
B12200Y.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.760
One moment, please.

05:45.040 --> 05:47.480
BOWLS

05:47.560 --> 05:49.360
This is one of our signature pieces.

05:49.440 --> 05:51.920
We've sold 84 pieces
since its spring launch.

05:52.520 --> 05:55.320
-Is there a customer named Sun Zhengyong?
-Let me check.

06:00.280 --> 06:02.960
Yes. Mr. Sun is our VIP client.

06:03.040 --> 06:05.840
On May 10th, he bought 11
of the same dress.

06:05.920 --> 06:07.640
Wait, no. Twelve.

06:07.720 --> 06:09.600
We gave him one as a freebie. Have a look.

06:10.360 --> 06:12.200
SALES DATE: MAY 10TH, SUN ZHENGYONG

06:14.440 --> 06:19.200
RETURNED 11 DRY-CLEANING VOUCHERS
RECEIVED ONE EXTRA DRESS

06:31.000 --> 06:32.520
Where's Captain Feng?
Didn't he want to see me?

06:32.600 --> 06:34.160
Officer He, he's in a task force meeting.

06:34.240 --> 06:35.120
He told me to wait here for you.

06:35.200 --> 06:36.440
This is Jin Manlang's statement
from this afternoon.

06:36.520 --> 06:37.520
Take a look.

06:37.600 --> 06:39.920
He denied that anyone
had hired him to kill.

06:40.000 --> 06:41.080
He claimed he only went
after Xu Meng and her dad

06:41.160 --> 06:42.160
to collect a debt.

06:43.960 --> 06:46.080
Jin Manlang has grown a pair.
He's trying to retract his confession.

06:46.160 --> 06:49.000
Officer He, there's more.
Jin Manlang said…

06:49.080 --> 06:50.880
What else did he say? Just say it.

06:51.680 --> 06:52.680
He said he's going to report you

06:52.760 --> 06:54.040
for forcing a confession.

06:56.680 --> 06:59.120
That Wolfie is unbelievable.

06:59.200 --> 07:00.400
He's pinning that on me.

07:00.480 --> 07:02.360
Bring him in. I want
to question him face-to-face.

07:02.440 --> 07:05.320
JIN MANLANG'S INTERROGATION RECORD

07:05.400 --> 07:07.960
JIN MANLANG, SECURITY DEPARTMENT
DEMOLITION DEPARTMENT

07:08.040 --> 07:09.480
LONGWEI GROUP

07:09.560 --> 07:10.400
‎2015

07:11.120 --> 07:12.240
It isn't ripe yet.

07:12.760 --> 07:14.080
Seriously.

07:15.040 --> 07:16.240
Pick another one for me.

07:16.320 --> 07:17.960
Just that one.

07:18.040 --> 07:18.960
RELOCATION BENEFITS ALL
SIGN EARLY, GAIN MORE

07:21.960 --> 07:23.800
-Give it here.
-It's not ripe. Why are you grabbing them?

07:23.880 --> 07:27.000
Come here, I said. Be in your position.

07:27.720 --> 07:28.600
Be in your position, okay?

07:29.520 --> 07:30.600
Keep your eyes peeled.

07:35.520 --> 07:36.560
Officer He.

07:37.920 --> 07:41.320
What brings you here, sir?

07:42.360 --> 07:43.480
Who are you?

07:45.280 --> 07:48.080
It's me. Lang. Lang.

07:49.600 --> 07:50.960
JIN MANLANG, SECURITY DEPARTMENT
DEMOLITION DEPARTMENT

07:52.680 --> 07:53.640
Look at you all cleaned up.

07:53.720 --> 07:55.600
You're a security manager now, huh?

07:55.680 --> 07:58.240
What? Running forced demolitions?

07:58.760 --> 07:59.920
No way.

08:00.760 --> 08:03.200
We keep things civil.

08:03.280 --> 08:05.040
We don't do dirty tricks.

08:05.120 --> 08:07.480
-What brings you here, Officer He?
-I'm here to observe.

08:08.960 --> 08:10.960
Right this way. Please come in.

08:15.360 --> 08:16.560
Welcome.

08:28.120 --> 08:29.040
Everyone,

08:29.560 --> 08:32.120
please let me go over this again.

08:32.200 --> 08:35.400
Longwei Group's compensation standards

08:35.480 --> 08:36.480
have always been consistent.

08:36.559 --> 08:37.720
Whether you move in early or late…

08:37.799 --> 08:39.760
Didn't someone say they'd
never come, no matter what?

08:40.360 --> 08:44.440
Now, you can take a look
at the notice in your hands.

08:44.520 --> 08:47.920
If you have any questions or doubts,

08:48.000 --> 08:50.040
come see me at the Redevelopment Bureau.

08:50.120 --> 08:51.040
My name is Qiao Suqing.

08:51.120 --> 08:52.000
Feng,

08:52.520 --> 08:55.840
doesn't that woman on stage look familiar?

08:55.920 --> 08:58.840
Wasn't she the mistress
from the fourth floor?

09:00.440 --> 09:02.600
Don't believe Du's nonsense.

09:02.680 --> 09:04.800
Qiao is a decent woman.

09:04.880 --> 09:07.040
She's now the finance director
at Longwei Real Estate.

09:07.720 --> 09:10.520
She's in charge of Yuanlongli's
demolition project.

09:10.600 --> 09:14.520
Also, if any household needs help moving,

09:14.600 --> 09:16.840
we'll do what we can to assist.

09:18.280 --> 09:20.120
The relocation service is a trap.

09:20.200 --> 09:21.200
Don't fall for it.

09:21.280 --> 09:24.040
QIAO SUQING

09:24.120 --> 09:25.320
Even a few hundred yuan would be too much.

09:48.320 --> 09:49.400
I can't talk him into it.

09:49.480 --> 09:51.240
Qiao, you're not an outsider here.

09:51.320 --> 09:53.160
You tell me. Should he stay or not?

09:56.560 --> 09:57.440
Mr. He,

09:57.520 --> 09:59.640
if even you can't convince him,

09:59.720 --> 10:01.360
I'm not in a position to say anything.

10:01.440 --> 10:03.120
Why not?

10:03.200 --> 10:05.160
He won't listen to me,

10:05.240 --> 10:06.640
but he might listen to you.

10:20.400 --> 10:21.520
You don't have to say it.

10:21.600 --> 10:23.720
I can tell from your eyes.

10:23.800 --> 10:25.480
You want him to stay.

10:28.800 --> 10:31.280
She's made herself pretty clear.

10:31.360 --> 10:32.720
Say something.

10:32.800 --> 10:35.440
Sir, don't put her on the spot.

10:35.520 --> 10:36.920
I'm definitely going back to Beijing.

10:37.000 --> 10:38.040
I have classes.

10:38.120 --> 10:40.240
You're the one
putting her in a tough spot.

10:40.840 --> 10:42.760
She wants you to stay.

10:42.840 --> 10:44.840
Don't play dumb.

10:58.000 --> 10:59.160
Mr. He,

11:00.680 --> 11:02.360
it's been so long.

11:04.200 --> 11:05.360
It's time

11:06.120 --> 11:07.040
to let go.

11:12.120 --> 11:14.440
You should let Ran go.

11:18.080 --> 11:20.200
What's wrong with you?
Why won't you ever say what you mean?

11:20.800 --> 11:22.080
-You clearly…
-Sir,

11:22.600 --> 11:24.000
just listen to her.

11:27.360 --> 11:29.720
Ran Fangxu, as your mentor,

11:29.800 --> 11:32.520
I'm ordering you to stay in Weiyang.

11:40.040 --> 11:42.080
TRAIN TICKET: WEIYANG TO BEIJING

11:42.160 --> 11:43.120
This is a ticket back to Beijing

11:44.360 --> 11:45.320
for tomorrow morning.

11:54.560 --> 11:55.800
Trying to walk back his own confession?

11:55.880 --> 11:56.720
‎1997

12:00.160 --> 12:04.240
SUN BOUGHT THE DRESS
I'LL CHECK THE CCTV IN YUANLONGLI. RAN

12:08.600 --> 12:10.600
When one door closes, another opens.

12:10.680 --> 12:12.400
There's always a way through.

12:15.560 --> 12:16.480
Captain Feng.

12:18.120 --> 12:20.200
Officer He, great job.

12:21.000 --> 12:23.720
You actually let the suspect
turn the tables on you.

12:25.320 --> 12:26.760
Let him make the noise for now.

12:26.840 --> 12:28.480
I'll have them list
everything out soon enough.

12:28.560 --> 12:29.400
No need to wait.

12:29.480 --> 12:31.680
Later, head to HR

12:31.760 --> 12:33.040
and process your transfer back.

12:33.120 --> 12:35.560
Also, get Ran over here.

12:35.640 --> 12:36.880
We're short-handed here.

12:39.040 --> 12:40.800
Captain Feng, don't.

12:42.000 --> 12:43.840
There's still one day left.

12:48.160 --> 12:50.560
You're the leader.
You have to keep your word.

12:50.640 --> 12:52.960
What can you do in one day?

12:53.040 --> 12:54.640
That's barely enough
for you to make a fuss about.

12:54.720 --> 12:57.200
Alright. Enough messing around.

12:57.280 --> 12:58.160
Get out of my sight.

12:58.760 --> 13:02.080
Captain Feng, I know
you're not really fed up with me.

13:02.160 --> 13:05.040
You're just annoyed
about that mining case.

13:05.120 --> 13:07.960
By the way, Ran brought in
a pickpocket yesterday.

13:08.040 --> 13:09.200
That guy, Luandongzi.

13:09.280 --> 13:11.760
The task force should follow up on him.

13:15.920 --> 13:17.120
-A pickpocket?
-Yeah.

13:17.200 --> 13:19.120
Ask if he's stashed a briefcase

13:19.200 --> 13:20.600
with "Qingsong Cement" on it.

13:20.680 --> 13:22.160
There's an important document inside.

13:22.240 --> 13:24.400
-That might be useful.
-He Yuanhang.

13:24.480 --> 13:27.760
Wait. What are you talking about?
What briefcase?

13:27.840 --> 13:29.560
He Yuanhang. Get back here!

13:59.520 --> 14:01.120
Sun Zhengyong isn't at the shop.

14:01.840 --> 14:04.680
But I did find something. On June 30th,
he suddenly shut the place down.

14:04.760 --> 14:06.800
That alone puts him on our radar.

14:06.880 --> 14:08.880
Mm. I'm pulling the CCTV from the 30th

14:08.960 --> 14:11.280
to check if he showed up
at Yuanlongli that day.

14:11.360 --> 14:13.280
Leave no stone unturned.

14:13.800 --> 14:14.840
Xinglong.

14:14.920 --> 14:16.280
Get me all the footage
from before the 30th.

14:17.560 --> 14:18.720
Got it.

14:20.760 --> 14:21.600
I'll make a call.

14:29.160 --> 14:31.760
-Hello?
-Hello? Qiao?

14:31.840 --> 14:34.080
-Officer He.
-Speaking.

14:34.160 --> 14:37.080
-Xiaohe's asleep.
-She's asleep?

14:37.160 --> 14:38.320
How about this?

14:38.400 --> 14:40.720
Could you let her stay
the night at your place?

14:40.800 --> 14:42.640
I'll have her grandma
pick her up tomorrow.

14:42.720 --> 14:43.760
Of course.

14:44.360 --> 14:47.520
Officer He, no need
to trouble her grandma.

14:47.600 --> 14:50.280
If you're fine with it,
give me the address.

14:50.360 --> 14:51.720
I'll send her there in the morning.

14:51.800 --> 14:54.080
I'm totally fine with it. Of course.

14:54.160 --> 14:56.680
Write this down. The address
is 102, Building Unit 2,

14:56.760 --> 14:58.320
Happiness Garden.

14:58.400 --> 15:00.400
Well, sorry to trouble you again.

15:00.480 --> 15:02.000
Not at all.

15:02.080 --> 15:04.720
Alright, I've got the address.

15:04.800 --> 15:07.200
I'll bring Xiaohe over
after breakfast tomorrow.

15:07.280 --> 15:09.280
-Sure. Thank you.
-No problem.

15:09.360 --> 15:10.200
I'll hang up now.

15:11.680 --> 15:13.880
I didn't know much about Qiao before.

15:14.880 --> 15:18.720
But she's really thoughtful

15:18.800 --> 15:20.480
and knows how to carry herself.

15:27.600 --> 15:29.240
There are only two people
breathing in this room.

15:29.320 --> 15:30.160
Don't pretend you didn't hear that.

15:31.800 --> 15:34.000
I heard you. Go on.

15:35.480 --> 15:36.760
Yuanlongli

15:36.840 --> 15:39.840
is either spreading superstitious nonsense
or making up rumors.

15:39.920 --> 15:42.240
Qiao is a decent person.

15:43.080 --> 15:44.720
How could they smear her as a mistress?

15:45.360 --> 15:47.200
They've gone too far. That's bullying.

15:47.280 --> 15:48.560
When I get the time,

15:48.640 --> 15:51.480
I'm going to clean up this toxic mess.

15:52.640 --> 15:53.960
Yeah, someone has to do that.

16:15.920 --> 16:18.040
Are you bringing in a video store here?

16:18.120 --> 16:19.760
Didn't you say you wanted everything?

16:21.040 --> 16:23.160
The footage from the past two weeks
is all here.

16:25.560 --> 16:26.680
Take your time.

16:39.040 --> 16:41.960
Xinglong, stop reading papers at night.

16:42.040 --> 16:42.960
You'll ruin your eyes.

16:43.720 --> 16:45.760
-Oh yeah?
-Let me ask you something.

16:49.280 --> 16:51.360
We're looking for this guy.

16:51.440 --> 16:52.320
Rat-faced.

16:53.120 --> 16:55.320
-Do you recognize him?
-No.

16:57.200 --> 16:58.320
That's fine.

16:58.400 --> 17:00.760
You can help us out.
Keep an eye out for him.

17:00.840 --> 17:02.400
Give your eyes a break too.

17:03.040 --> 17:05.040
You call this a break?

17:05.880 --> 17:07.680
Hey. I'm on duty here.

17:09.319 --> 17:11.119
There's a reward if you find him.

17:12.920 --> 17:14.480
Then I'll help.

17:17.160 --> 17:18.079
Come.

17:21.359 --> 17:22.599
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

17:34.520 --> 17:36.480
If you spot anyone familiar
or suspicious, call me right away.

17:37.440 --> 17:38.480
Got it.

17:39.640 --> 17:40.840
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

18:04.200 --> 18:06.960
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

18:26.680 --> 18:28.680
No. No. My eyes are going blurry.

18:29.200 --> 18:31.000
I need to go out and get some air.

18:31.080 --> 18:32.320
My eyes are shot too.

18:33.040 --> 18:34.680
You're young. How could your eyes be shot?

18:34.760 --> 18:36.880
-Keep watching.
-Everything's blurry.

18:37.640 --> 18:38.480
Keep watching.

18:38.560 --> 18:41.480
If it gets that bad,
have Officer Ran buy you some lamb liver.

18:41.560 --> 18:42.680
They're good for the eyes.

18:48.600 --> 18:49.560
He.

18:50.960 --> 18:52.720
What's wrong? Are your eyes blurry too?

18:52.800 --> 18:53.920
It's not that. Look.

18:58.760 --> 19:00.920
Got him? Which day?

19:01.000 --> 19:04.120
June 27th. 1:23 p.m.

19:04.200 --> 19:05.960
That lines up. Everything lines up.

19:06.040 --> 19:07.920
On the 27th, Sun Zhengyong

19:08.000 --> 19:10.080
scoped out the Qihuang Clinic
on the 17th floor.

19:10.160 --> 19:11.520
He found out it had shut down.

19:11.600 --> 19:12.840
Then he tricked Xu Meng

19:12.920 --> 19:14.480
into bringing her dad there
for treatment on the 30th.

19:14.560 --> 19:15.960
After that, he tipped off the person

19:16.040 --> 19:19.640
who hired Wolfie
and set him up to take the fall.

19:19.720 --> 19:20.960
Meanwhile, he hid in the building

19:21.040 --> 19:22.840
and waited for his chance
to move in on Xu Meng and her dad.

19:22.920 --> 19:24.280
It all checks out.

19:27.960 --> 19:31.720
But Xu Meng and her dad
took the elevator to the 18th floor.

19:31.800 --> 19:33.120
How did he know that in advance?

19:33.200 --> 19:34.760
Isn't that obvious?

19:34.840 --> 19:37.800
He told Xu Meng the clinic
had moved to the 18th floor.

19:40.120 --> 19:42.600
Then how did he wipe his tracks?

19:43.360 --> 19:45.280
Why are you back
to playing "20 Questions"?

19:45.360 --> 19:47.080
I'll track down his address right now,

19:47.160 --> 19:49.600
drag him in front of you,
and let him explain it himself.

19:49.680 --> 19:50.520
Wait for me.

19:53.240 --> 19:54.640
If I can't find him, I…

19:54.720 --> 19:55.880
Wait. Hold on.

19:57.000 --> 19:59.160
Ran. He. It's him.

19:59.840 --> 20:00.760
I… It's him!

20:01.360 --> 20:02.920
That rat-faced guy.

20:05.800 --> 20:07.240
Which day's footage is this?

20:07.320 --> 20:08.480
This isn't footage.

20:08.560 --> 20:10.080
It's live.

20:13.600 --> 20:14.400
Quick.

20:14.480 --> 20:15.640
-Quick.
-Let's go.

20:18.880 --> 20:20.440
-Seventeenth floor. Seventeenth.
-No.

20:21.200 --> 20:23.560
Get off at 16th. Hit both elevators
down to the first floor,

20:23.640 --> 20:25.040
then take the stairs up to the 17th.

20:25.120 --> 20:26.400
We box him in from two sides.

20:28.360 --> 20:31.480
He, you're indeed an expert
in making arrests on-site.

20:32.800 --> 20:35.120
You still have a lot more
to learn. Alright?

20:35.200 --> 20:36.920
But I don't get it.

20:37.000 --> 20:39.440
What's he doing back
at Yuanlongli right now?

20:40.520 --> 20:42.080
I read this somewhere.

20:42.160 --> 20:45.440
Murderers and lovers
tend to revisit the scene.

20:45.520 --> 20:46.360
I didn't know that.

20:47.640 --> 20:49.000
You still have a lot more to learn.

21:03.920 --> 21:07.360
QIHUANG CLINIC

21:16.760 --> 21:17.800
Sun Zhengyong.

21:19.840 --> 21:20.920
Police.

21:21.440 --> 21:24.400
Stop. Ran, he's heading your way.

21:41.120 --> 21:42.120
Ran Fangxu,

21:42.640 --> 21:45.640
taking down suspects
is basic police training.

21:45.720 --> 21:47.480
You need to get past this.

21:47.560 --> 21:48.720
What?

21:55.880 --> 21:57.960
How did you pass
your physical training test?

21:59.360 --> 22:01.680
Shut up. Steady your breathing.
Face him head-on.

22:06.880 --> 22:09.240
Horse stance. Turn into a side lunge.
Block. Trip him.

22:11.880 --> 22:14.360
Shout. Feint a punch.
Knee strike to the abdomen.

22:26.280 --> 22:27.080
Got him.

22:31.720 --> 22:32.760
Still trying to run?

22:33.960 --> 22:36.560
He, thanks for the coaching.

22:37.840 --> 22:38.720
Have some faith.

22:39.760 --> 22:40.600
Are you okay?

22:43.080 --> 22:48.200
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

22:48.280 --> 22:49.200
MIRROR

22:50.200 --> 22:51.480
-Over here.
-Move.

22:59.320 --> 23:01.000
-Captain Feng.
-Captain Feng.

23:03.320 --> 23:04.400
Did you crack the case?

23:05.080 --> 23:05.920
We still need to interrogate him.

23:09.200 --> 23:10.120
Upstairs.

23:22.600 --> 23:23.640
Sun Zhengyong,

23:24.840 --> 23:26.160
let's not waste time.

23:26.240 --> 23:27.200
Where's Xu Meng?

23:27.800 --> 23:28.640
Xu Meng?

23:32.720 --> 23:34.640
Do you mean Mengmeng?

23:34.720 --> 23:36.000
Where's Mengmeng?

23:36.080 --> 23:37.760
She took her dad and left.

23:37.840 --> 23:40.040
They bought train tickets for July 1st.

23:43.400 --> 23:44.760
Did you see them leave?

23:44.840 --> 23:45.800
No.

23:45.880 --> 23:48.280
One day, she came to me

23:48.960 --> 23:50.160
and asked to borrow some money.

23:50.240 --> 23:51.280
When?

23:51.360 --> 23:54.000
Around late June.

23:55.200 --> 23:58.040
She said someone was threatening her
and wanted her dead.

23:58.560 --> 24:01.160
So she planned to take her dad
and get out of here for good.

24:01.240 --> 24:02.640
But she was worried

24:02.720 --> 24:04.600
the trip would be too much for her dad.

24:05.200 --> 24:09.200
So before leaving, she wanted
to take him to Qihuang Clinic for therapy.

24:09.800 --> 24:11.720
She sounded so pitiful.

24:12.240 --> 24:13.560
I lent her 30,000.

24:13.640 --> 24:15.040
I didn't expect her

24:15.120 --> 24:17.840
to disappear right after taking the money.

24:20.360 --> 24:22.200
Where did you hide them?

24:22.280 --> 24:23.840
I didn't.

24:26.880 --> 24:28.960
Officer, did something happen

24:29.560 --> 24:31.080
to Mengmeng?

24:32.080 --> 24:34.080
You lent her that much money.

24:34.160 --> 24:35.400
What's your relationship?

24:36.280 --> 24:37.440
I like her.

24:37.520 --> 24:39.040
How do you like her?

24:39.640 --> 24:43.040
You know what she does for a living.

24:43.880 --> 24:45.920
I'd book her all the time.

24:46.000 --> 24:48.520
One day, I got drunk.

24:48.600 --> 24:50.360
I told her I wanted to go out with her.

24:50.880 --> 24:54.000
She thought I was talking nonsense
and turned me down.

24:54.080 --> 24:57.080
I was mad. We got into an argument.

24:57.160 --> 24:58.600
And then you forced yourself on her?

24:58.680 --> 25:00.240
No, I didn't. No.

25:00.320 --> 25:03.200
-Did you buy Xu Meng clothes?
-Yeah.

25:04.400 --> 25:05.960
Did you give her a dress from Bowls?

25:06.040 --> 25:08.080
Bowls?

25:11.080 --> 25:12.480
Maybe.

25:13.360 --> 25:15.360
I often go to malls.

25:15.440 --> 25:19.480
When big brands go on sale, I stock up.

25:19.560 --> 25:21.920
First, it makes good gifts for girls.

25:22.000 --> 25:24.080
Second, I can copy the design

25:24.680 --> 25:26.240
and get my money back.

25:28.840 --> 25:29.960
Sun Zhengyong,

25:30.880 --> 25:31.920
you can spin tall tales.

25:32.000 --> 25:34.920
No matter how well you spin it,
it's still a story.

25:35.000 --> 25:36.240
Tell me.

25:36.320 --> 25:39.080
Why did you suddenly
shut your shop on the 30th?

25:39.160 --> 25:43.000
And why were you on the 17th floor
of New York Block on the 27th?

25:43.840 --> 25:45.280
Then this morning,

25:45.360 --> 25:47.320
you went back to No. 1713 again.

25:47.400 --> 25:48.760
And you ran when you saw us.

25:48.840 --> 25:51.360
Try making up a story for all that.

25:56.160 --> 25:57.120
Feeling guilty?

25:58.200 --> 25:59.320
Go on.

25:59.840 --> 26:01.880
I have plenty more evidence
to help you fill in the blanks.

26:01.960 --> 26:02.920
I…

26:03.680 --> 26:04.800
I can't hold it anymore.

26:04.880 --> 26:07.480
Then talk. Where's Xu Meng?

26:07.560 --> 26:08.800
That's not what I meant.

26:09.640 --> 26:11.000
I need the bathroom.

26:11.720 --> 26:13.840
I have prostate issues.

26:13.920 --> 26:15.280
I can't hold it in.

26:15.360 --> 26:19.000
And just now, this officer kicked me.

26:19.080 --> 26:21.320
I really can't take it anymore.

26:25.520 --> 26:27.400
I'm about to burst.

26:31.520 --> 26:34.520
DUTY AND SELF-RESTRAINT
RIGHTEOUSNESS AND PEACE

26:34.600 --> 26:35.440
Look who it is.

26:35.520 --> 26:37.360
The famous Officer He.

26:38.080 --> 26:39.360
Still with the Criminal Department?

26:39.440 --> 26:40.880
Not coming back?

26:40.960 --> 26:42.880
Of course. This is
where the big cases are.

26:42.960 --> 26:46.600
Unlike someone who couldn't
even handle public order.

26:46.680 --> 26:47.800
Keep bragging. Go on.

26:47.880 --> 26:49.160
Big cases? How big?

26:49.240 --> 26:50.480
Bigger than a task force case?

26:50.560 --> 26:52.600
Do you have to give proper case briefings?

26:52.680 --> 26:54.520
You're just someone
stringing up police tape,

26:54.600 --> 26:55.840
and now you're talking
task force briefings?

26:55.920 --> 26:57.400
You sure have a knack
for blowing your own trumpet.

26:57.480 --> 26:58.480
And you're any better?

26:58.560 --> 27:00.680
Still chasing that prank case, aren't you?

27:00.760 --> 27:02.480
Come on. Let me see.
What big suspect did you catch?

27:04.400 --> 27:05.520
Officer Qu.

27:06.280 --> 27:08.640
He Yuanhang, are you trying to amuse me?

27:09.480 --> 27:10.920
A criminal investigator like you

27:11.000 --> 27:12.720
is actually busting
a street vendor selling fakes?

27:14.880 --> 27:16.600
Officer Qu, do you know this guy?

27:17.200 --> 27:18.440
He's Mr. Sun.

27:18.520 --> 27:21.080
He shows up at the station twice a week.

27:21.160 --> 27:22.240
Busier than Officer He.

27:23.280 --> 27:24.120
A week?

27:24.200 --> 27:26.440
-When was he brought in?
-Last week.

27:27.080 --> 27:28.360
June 29th.

27:28.440 --> 27:30.640
He was selling counterfeit goods
and got into a fight.

27:30.720 --> 27:32.800
He was brought in and held for five days.

27:39.320 --> 27:42.680
You suspect he has something to do
with that prank case?

27:45.320 --> 27:47.800
I can vouch for him. It wasn't him.

27:48.400 --> 27:49.320
He didn't have the time.

27:58.600 --> 28:02.960
Officer, if I don't go now,
I'm going to piss myself.

28:06.000 --> 28:09.400
DUTY AND SELF-RESTRAINT
RIGHTEOUSNESS AND PEACE

28:16.520 --> 28:17.680
Officer,

28:18.320 --> 28:20.160
about the first question from earlier,

28:20.240 --> 28:21.920
you already know the answer.

28:22.000 --> 28:25.280
Now I'll answer the second and third.

28:25.360 --> 28:29.040
I ran when I saw you because I panicked.

28:29.120 --> 28:32.000
I thought you were after
my counterfeit business.

28:32.080 --> 28:34.480
As for the 17th floor at New York Block,

28:34.560 --> 28:37.800
there's a tailor there I work with.

28:37.880 --> 28:40.600
Last week, I took the fabric
to make samples.

28:41.200 --> 28:43.880
This morning, I went to collect
the finished goods.

28:43.960 --> 28:45.960
But when I got to the 17th,

28:46.040 --> 28:49.240
I didn't know why, something just hit me.

28:49.320 --> 28:50.520
I suddenly thought of Mengmeng.

28:51.360 --> 28:53.760
So I figured I'd check out Qihuang Clinic.

28:53.840 --> 28:57.720
I didn't know it had shut down.

28:57.800 --> 29:00.120
Mengmeng played me.

29:00.200 --> 29:02.320
That's enough. You don't need to go on.

29:02.960 --> 29:07.040
You really shouldn't
get too close to unlucky people.

29:07.120 --> 29:09.360
Bad luck spreads like a disease.

29:09.440 --> 29:11.200
Once it sticks, it rubs off.

29:13.360 --> 29:17.000
Officer, did Mengmeng go missing?

29:18.240 --> 29:20.320
That might be the best outcome

29:20.840 --> 29:22.480
for the people around her.

29:22.560 --> 29:25.000
Enough said. Spare me the act.

29:25.080 --> 29:26.160
You're no saint yourself.

29:26.240 --> 29:27.440
You're too rotten
for bad luck to touch you.

29:30.120 --> 29:31.240
Can you take these off now?

29:53.960 --> 29:55.840
-Mr. Song.
-What is it?

29:55.920 --> 29:57.320
Cripple Du's men were tailing me.

29:57.400 --> 29:58.920
Just as I dug the body up,

29:59.000 --> 30:01.520
they snatched it and took my car.

30:02.880 --> 30:05.440
-What did you just say?
-I'm telling the truth.

30:05.520 --> 30:07.680
Look at this. My head
has been thrashed badly.

30:30.560 --> 30:31.400
Who sent this over?

30:42.920 --> 30:44.400
-Who?
-Song Qingsong,

30:45.360 --> 30:46.760
did you see the photo?

30:48.240 --> 30:50.920
Director Li, what photo? I have no idea.

30:51.000 --> 30:52.800
Stop pretending.

30:52.880 --> 30:55.280
That photo was left right at my doorstep.

30:56.400 --> 30:57.280
Song Qingsong,

30:57.800 --> 30:59.440
I don't care if you make dirty money.

31:00.280 --> 31:01.960
But you actually killed someone.

31:03.560 --> 31:05.440
Director Li, hear me out.

31:05.520 --> 31:07.480
Someone has died! Hear you out for what?

31:08.280 --> 31:10.840
Listen carefully. Go on the run.

31:10.920 --> 31:12.600
-Right now.
-Alright. Drop the act.

31:12.680 --> 31:13.720
What did you say?

31:14.400 --> 31:16.360
Did you get Cripple Du to take my car

31:17.200 --> 31:18.920
and have someone seal the bid document?

31:19.000 --> 31:20.360
Song Qingsong.

31:20.880 --> 31:21.640
-I…
-Li.

31:21.720 --> 31:23.400
Listen up.

31:23.480 --> 31:25.760
I didn't burn the bid you sold me.

31:25.840 --> 31:27.040
So here are your options.

31:27.120 --> 31:31.520
One, I keep Dongshan Mine
and you tell Cripple Du to get lost.

31:32.160 --> 31:33.960
Second, you return the eight million.

31:34.040 --> 31:35.960
Otherwise, we both go down together.

31:36.040 --> 31:37.640
We all go down together!

31:37.720 --> 31:39.280
Song Qingsong,

31:39.360 --> 31:41.960
between bribery and murder,
which one carries the heavier sentence?

31:42.040 --> 31:43.480
We're not going down together.

31:43.560 --> 31:45.000
I'm not scared!

31:45.080 --> 31:46.280
I have money.

31:46.360 --> 31:48.200
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

31:48.280 --> 31:50.640
What can you do to me? What can you do?

31:57.600 --> 32:00.360
I'm not scared! I have money.

32:00.440 --> 32:02.360
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

32:02.440 --> 32:05.600
What can you do to me? What can you do?

32:07.560 --> 32:10.160
I'm not scared! I have money.

32:10.240 --> 32:11.920
I could kill more and still
find someone to take the fall.

32:12.000 --> 32:14.320
What can you do to me? What can you do?

32:15.600 --> 32:17.000
Song Qingsong,

32:17.520 --> 32:20.360
you're not just ignorant of the law,
you are stupid.

32:20.440 --> 32:21.280
Son of a bitch.

32:21.360 --> 32:23.040
You are despicable.

32:23.560 --> 32:25.760
Now I'll give you two options.

32:25.840 --> 32:27.080
One, I burn the photo,

32:27.760 --> 32:28.720
you go out and lie low for a while.

32:29.320 --> 32:33.000
Two, I hand the photo and the recording
over to the police.

32:33.520 --> 32:36.880
Keep both your money and your life
or lose everything. Your call.

32:39.160 --> 32:41.360
Mr… Mr. Song. Mr. Song. Mr. Song.

32:41.440 --> 32:44.160
I was wrong. Mr. Song. Forgive me.

32:44.680 --> 32:47.000
-It's my fault.
-All of you

32:47.800 --> 32:49.400
are trying to screw me over.

32:49.480 --> 32:51.480
Mr. Song. Forgive me.

33:23.480 --> 33:25.280
WEIYANG CITY DONGSHAN MINE BID DOCUMENT

33:36.160 --> 33:38.000
Book me two tickets to Los Angeles.

33:38.880 --> 33:40.040
As soon as possible.

33:40.680 --> 33:42.880
Got it, Mr. Song. Who's going with you?

33:51.320 --> 33:54.120
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

33:56.600 --> 33:59.440
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY

34:10.080 --> 34:12.239
Mr. Song. Cripple Du's men are here.

34:13.920 --> 34:14.760
Go.

34:17.400 --> 34:18.960
‎-Stop!
‎-Don't run!

34:19.040 --> 34:20.679
‎-Stay there!
‎-Don't run!

34:27.840 --> 34:29.199
Qingsong. Take the back door.

34:29.280 --> 34:30.239
We leave together.

34:30.320 --> 34:32.360
Too late. We don't have time. Qingsong.

34:32.440 --> 34:34.280
Don't worry, Qingsong.
The police won't trace it here.

34:34.360 --> 34:37.040
Even if they do,
I'll take the fall. Go now.

34:38.239 --> 34:40.120
As long as you, my sister,
and your child are safe,

34:40.199 --> 34:41.679
even if I take a bullet for it,

34:41.760 --> 34:43.040
it'll be worth it.

34:43.120 --> 34:46.320
Shanlong, after I'm gone,
you're the factory director.

34:46.920 --> 34:48.239
Take care of everything for me.

34:48.840 --> 34:51.400
-Qingsong, go. Qingsong, go.
-I'll be back.

34:51.480 --> 34:53.000
-I'll be back.
-Go, Qingsong.

34:53.080 --> 34:54.920
Qingsong, go.

34:58.520 --> 34:59.640
‎Fucking hell!

35:07.200 --> 35:09.720
Stop! Stop! Stop!

35:23.640 --> 35:25.720
I paid you to put on a show.

35:26.240 --> 35:28.120
You're actually beating me?

35:28.200 --> 35:31.520
For real? How dare you!

35:31.600 --> 35:32.560
Fuck.

35:32.640 --> 35:34.480
Motherfuckers.

35:36.960 --> 35:38.400
Can you be professional?

36:23.480 --> 36:25.040
You got lucky this time.

36:25.800 --> 36:28.040
It's not going to happen a third time.

36:48.080 --> 36:53.240
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

36:53.320 --> 36:55.880
INTERROGATION ROOM

37:02.600 --> 37:04.400
I was trying to prove myself.

37:04.480 --> 37:05.680
But then,

37:06.360 --> 37:08.160
I proved I was a fool.

37:11.040 --> 37:13.560
Now our only lead is Song Qingsong.

37:15.800 --> 37:18.800
-Let's go.
-Hurry up. Quit dragging your feet.

37:19.480 --> 37:21.440
Officer, my leg hurts.

37:21.520 --> 37:22.600
Wu Shanlong?

37:23.520 --> 37:26.400
FAIR AND JUST

37:27.560 --> 37:28.840
Good day, officers.

37:29.600 --> 37:31.600
-What's he in for?
-It's a misunderstanding.

37:32.120 --> 37:34.000
-Misunderstanding.
-Did they ask you?

37:35.280 --> 37:38.400
It's about Dongshan Mine.
We'll need to question him further.

37:38.480 --> 37:39.600
Have you arrested Song Qingsong?

37:39.680 --> 37:40.920
Reporting, sir.

37:41.680 --> 37:42.640
From now on,

37:42.720 --> 37:44.920
there'll be no more
Song Qingsong in Weiyang.

37:45.000 --> 37:46.200
End of report.

37:48.080 --> 37:49.080
Move.

37:59.960 --> 38:04.000
RUICHUAN RESTAURANT

38:05.480 --> 38:07.040
One faked you out,

38:07.560 --> 38:08.800
the other got away.

38:09.680 --> 38:13.000
These two are cunning.

38:14.280 --> 38:15.320
Stop reading.

38:15.920 --> 38:16.760
He got away.

38:16.840 --> 38:18.400
What's the point of staring
at the notebook?

38:18.480 --> 38:19.560
Eat the noodles. Come on.

38:24.440 --> 38:25.800
Stop reading.

38:25.880 --> 38:27.080
Listen.

38:27.160 --> 38:29.040
We're putting this case on hold for now.

38:29.120 --> 38:31.240
I've talked to Captain Feng.

38:31.320 --> 38:32.360
After this meal,

38:32.440 --> 38:34.000
you report to the Task Force.

38:34.080 --> 38:35.080
As for me,

38:35.840 --> 38:37.200
I'm going back to the station.

38:54.240 --> 38:55.160
He,

38:56.520 --> 38:57.400
are you backing out?

38:59.920 --> 39:01.600
How can you call this backing out?

39:01.680 --> 39:05.080
This is getting back to where we belong
and doing our part.

39:05.160 --> 39:06.480
Getting back is backing out.

39:08.400 --> 39:10.880
We've taken a beating over a missing case
that hasn't even been filed.

39:10.960 --> 39:13.520
And now you say don't back out,
tell me how we move forward.

39:14.560 --> 39:16.640
Besides, we had an agreement
with Captain Feng.

39:16.720 --> 39:19.720
Today's the third day.
We have to keep our word.

39:20.640 --> 39:21.560
We still have tonight.

39:22.560 --> 39:25.080
Ran Fangxu, are you stupid or what?

39:26.040 --> 39:27.960
The task force has brought in Wu Shanlong.

39:28.040 --> 39:30.040
If you don't report in now,
forget the credit,

39:30.120 --> 39:31.640
you won't even get a shred of it.

39:31.720 --> 39:33.920
I didn't become a cop for credit.

39:34.000 --> 39:36.480
I owe Xu Meng and her dad the truth.

39:51.240 --> 39:54.040
He, after everything we've done,

39:54.800 --> 39:57.440
if we pull out now,
it'll all be for nothing.

39:57.960 --> 39:59.200
Let me tell you this.

40:00.640 --> 40:03.880
I've lived long enough to learn one thing.

40:04.480 --> 40:05.920
Don't get too hung up on things.

40:06.000 --> 40:07.840
Let go when you can.

40:07.920 --> 40:10.480
Or else, you'll drive yourself crazy.

40:27.960 --> 40:30.120
Looks like my first case

40:31.360 --> 40:32.720
is going to end in failure.

40:40.440 --> 40:42.680
Ever since I entered PPSUC,

40:43.440 --> 40:45.680
I've been studying all kinds
of missing person cases.

40:47.840 --> 40:49.200
I told myself that once
I became a police officer

40:50.000 --> 40:51.640
and took on a case,

40:51.720 --> 40:54.120
I'd find the missing person at all costs

40:55.280 --> 40:56.840
and leave no regrets.

41:01.080 --> 41:03.840
I thought I knew my stuff.

41:04.440 --> 41:06.080
But when it comes to real fieldwork,

41:08.560 --> 41:09.520
I'm nothing.

41:22.000 --> 41:23.000
That's funny.

41:24.080 --> 41:25.120
You know what?

41:26.440 --> 41:28.520
My first case
was a missing persons case too.

41:28.600 --> 41:31.160
It was an old man with dementia.

41:32.120 --> 41:33.680
I ran around for days,

41:33.760 --> 41:35.480
nearly wore my shoes out.

41:39.600 --> 41:40.880
So you failed too?

41:44.800 --> 41:46.000
I ran out of leads

41:46.800 --> 41:47.800
and had to try something stupid.

42:01.520 --> 42:02.880
Enough with the suspense.

42:03.960 --> 42:05.400
No. It's not that.

42:06.840 --> 42:07.720
Here's what I did.

42:08.560 --> 42:11.120
I pretended to be the old man

42:11.200 --> 42:13.920
and followed his way of thinking.

42:14.000 --> 42:14.880
I wandered around aimlessly.

42:14.960 --> 42:17.360
When I was hungry,
I grabbed whatever I could find.

42:17.440 --> 42:18.760
When I needed to pee,

42:18.840 --> 42:20.000
I just went wherever.

42:21.480 --> 42:22.360
And in the end,

42:22.440 --> 42:24.520
I actually found him.

42:28.360 --> 42:29.800
He.

42:29.880 --> 42:31.800
That's basically immersive roleplay.

42:34.280 --> 42:36.080
Yeah. Right.

42:37.680 --> 42:38.600
I came up with this myself

42:39.720 --> 42:41.360
22 years before you.

42:46.320 --> 42:49.240
How about we…

42:55.080 --> 42:56.360
No way.

42:59.400 --> 43:00.760
Listen.

43:00.840 --> 43:02.120
If you want to do that, go ahead.

43:02.200 --> 43:04.320
Anyone who goes with you
is out of their mind.

43:09.960 --> 43:10.960
NOTEBOOK

43:47.880 --> 43:49.760
Can you not breathe all over me?

43:49.840 --> 43:50.880
What?

43:51.400 --> 43:54.320
That old man in the footage
kept his head down like this.

43:55.400 --> 43:57.240
You smell like garlic.

43:57.320 --> 43:59.320
Focus on your job.

44:17.960 --> 44:20.360
Focus on your job. Lean back.

44:20.440 --> 44:21.800
You're getting back at me.

44:38.360 --> 44:40.200
Why are your legs shaking?

44:40.280 --> 44:42.440
You should lose some weight.

44:42.520 --> 44:43.720
If you can't handle it, I'll switch.

44:43.800 --> 44:45.200
Don't move.

44:45.280 --> 44:47.440
If we can't get it right this time,
we run it again.

44:52.440 --> 44:54.320
-I'm taking my jacket off.
-Steady.

45:04.720 --> 45:05.840
PRIVATE ROOM 1

45:06.880 --> 45:07.880
Hey.

45:07.960 --> 45:10.160
Have you picked up anything so far?

45:10.880 --> 45:11.800
No.

45:12.320 --> 45:14.840
Have you felt anything back there?

45:15.600 --> 45:16.600
I have.

45:17.360 --> 45:18.240
What is it?

45:18.320 --> 45:20.400
Xu Meng has better stamina than you.

45:28.960 --> 45:30.040
I may not have gone to the Police Academy,

45:30.760 --> 45:32.960
but I've been a cop for 22 years.

45:33.040 --> 45:35.160
I have my own ways of working things out.

45:35.760 --> 45:36.680
Let's hear it.

45:37.520 --> 45:39.920
Everything is always changing.
We only have so much energy.

45:40.000 --> 45:41.400
Focus on the big picture.
Don't dwell on the small stuff.

45:41.480 --> 45:43.040
Dress well, eat well.

45:43.640 --> 45:44.520
I understand the first three.

45:45.200 --> 45:46.840
What's that last one supposed to mean?

45:47.360 --> 45:50.240
Simple. What can't you live without?

45:50.320 --> 45:51.600
Eat, drink, sleep, and poop.

45:51.680 --> 45:53.160
It's in those everyday things

45:53.240 --> 45:54.680
that people slip up and leave traces.

45:54.760 --> 45:56.640
Take this cola.

45:56.720 --> 45:58.960
You pop it open, and it sprays everywhere.
You shake it off, right?

45:59.040 --> 46:02.880
And when you do, you leave a trail. Right?

46:05.080 --> 46:06.160
What are you looking at?

46:06.240 --> 46:08.880
He. Look. What's that?

46:11.840 --> 46:14.480
Isn't that where I shook off
the cola last time?

46:14.560 --> 46:15.680
No.

46:15.760 --> 46:17.480
Look higher. Up there.

